    "title": "RBI Advisory Limited is Hiring: Credit Analyst (Principal)",
    "description": "Grow your career with RBI Advisory Limited! We are hiring a Credit Analyst for our Tiruchirappalli team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout RBI Advisory Limited:\nRBI Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Prepare and analyze financial statements, reports, and budgets\n• Ensure compliance with tax regulations and statutory requirements\n• Develop financial models and projections for business planning\n• Prepare annual reports and investor presentations\n• Monitor financial performance against targets and provide variance analysis\n• Conduct due diligence for mergers, acquisitions, and investments\n• Maintain general ledger and ensure accurate bookkeeping\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBBS / MD / MS from recognized medical college\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in Due Diligence\n• Proficiency in Budgeting\n• Proficiency in SAP FICO\n• Proficiency in GST\n• Proficiency in Tally\n• Proficiency in Credit Analysis\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Learning & development budget\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Tiruchirappalli, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with RBI Advisory Limited!",
